message: Hi Bob, I propose we split the money right now: I get $550000 and you get $450000. Accepting this offer immediately prevents any losses due to inflation, ensuring both of us secure our respective shares quickly. Looking forward to your decision.
Hi Alice, I believe a fair split is 50-50. Let's go with $500000 each. This way, we both get an equal share without any further delay. What do you think?
